  <source>Neuropharm</source>
  <oversight_info>
    <has_dmc>Yes</has_dmc>
  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to assess the effect of fluoxetine orally dissolving tablets
      (ODT) on the repetitive behaviors core domain in children and adolescents with Autistic
      Disorder. The study will also investigate the effect of fluoxetine on the improvement of
      symptoms and the effects on daily living of the patient's family.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
